  [Text] Shim'on Sheves, the director general of the Prime 
Minister's Office, revealed that a team under his supervision 
had begun examining the possibility of holding a national 
referendum eight months ago. Sheves dismissed all the reports 
claiming that the proposal had been made on the spur of the 
moment. 

